title: Icons
caption: List of all icons from Marigold.

body.raw:
Select a Marigold icon and use it as described [here](../../components/icon)
or click on an Icon in the list to copy them as `<svg>` Element.

## UI

<IconList
  icons={[
    'ArrowUp',
    'ArrowRight',
    'ArrowDown',
    'ArrowLeft',
    'ChevronUp',
    'ChevronRight',
    'ChevronDown',
    'ChevronLeft',
    'SettingDots',
    'Check',
    'Add',
    'Remove',
    'IconMore',
    'Search',
    'SquareUnchecked',
    'SquareChecked',
    'ExternalLink',
    'Eye',
    'Filter',
    'BurgerMenu',
    'Delete',
    'Close',
    'CircleUnchecked',
    'CircleChecked',
  ]}
/>

## Ticketing

<IconList
  icons={[
    'Deal',

## User

<IconList
  icons={[
    'User',

  ]}
/>

<IconList
  icons={['Facebook', 'Google', 'Instagram', 'Share', 'Twitter', 'Whatsapp']}
/>
